 algorithm to calculate the spin susceptibility of impurity for\narbitrary structured bands, while negating the applicability of Wilson's\ndefinition to such cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2015 14:34:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2015 10:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2015 14:16:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-21"}
