 illuminated hemisphere model that is based on\nthe idea that the emission originates primarily from the side of the primary\nfacing the hot companion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2015 14:39:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-23"}
